goa is a 2015 indian kannada romantic comedy film directed by surya . it stars komal kumar , tarun chandra , srikanth , sharmila mandre , sonu and british theatre artiste rachel &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; in lead roles . the film is an official remake of the tamil film of the same title ( 2010 ) directed by venkat prabhu . the film features the music composed by arjun janya whilst the cinematography is by rajesh katta .